reviews.review_text: Harsh, high-pitched recording of a mediocre show.
Thanks Jim The sound flows beautifully! There is no limit the joys which abound, and I think that this is an overall good show- great sound

njpg sucks This is a pretty decent recording, is definitely not high-pitched and the show is quite good. No there is no Dark Star and I would knock this pull only for not recording D/S but hey. You know njpg listened to 30 seconds of Stranger then went on to slam the next recording. F%*king pr*ck
